<div class="proposal_wrapper--add">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12">
      <div class="proposal_topbar">
        <div class="col m6 pull-m6 s12">
          <h1 class="proposal_title">Edit Your Offer</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col m6 s12">
      <form class="proposal_add-wrapper" action="/proposals/{{proposal.id}}?_method=PUT" method="post"
        id="editproposal" onsubmit="return checkForm(this);">
          <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PUT">
          <div class="col m6 s12">
              <p>Start by pasting the URL for the Instagram image you wish to use when you announce your offer. It should look something like
              https://www.instagram.com/p/<strong>(the unique ID/URL of the photo)</strong>/</p>
            <div class="input-field">
              <input type="text" name="offerLink" value="{{proposal.offerLink}}">
              <label for="offerLink">Instagram Announcement Link</label>
            </div>

          <p>Describe how and where you plan to use the photo.</p>
          <div class="input-field">
            <input type="text" name="usage" value="{{proposal.usage}}" placeholder="i.e. Instagram, Website, Print, etc.">
          </div>
          {{!-- <div class="input-field">
            <select name="status">
              {{#select proposal.status}}
                <option value="public" selected>Public</option>
                <option value="private">Private</option>
                <option value="unpublished">Unpublished</option>
              {{/select}}
            </select>
            <label for="status">Status</label>
          </div>   --}}
          <p>
            <p>Will the creator be mentioned when the photo is used?</p>
            <p>
          <label>Credit</label>
          <div class="switch">
            <label>
            No
            <input type="checkbox" name="credit" id="credit" {{#if proposal.credit}} checked="checked" {{/if}}>
            <span class="lever"></span>
            Yes
            </label>
          </div>
          </p>
          </p>
          <p>
            <p>Do you want to accept images as they come in or allow as many submissions for your offer</p>
            <label>approval Needed</label>
            <div class="switch">
              <label>
              No
              <input type="checkbox" name="approvalNeeded" id="approvalNeeded" {{#if proposal.approvalNeeded}} checked="checked" {{/if}}>
              <span class="lever"></span>
              Yes
              </label>
            </div>
          </p>
          <p>You may offer any form of compensation. ex. 1 ice-cream with 2 toppings</p>
          <div class="input-field">
            <input type="text" name="compensation" value="{{proposal.compensation}}">
          </div>
          <p>Below you can greet your customer and inform them what is going on in this page</p>
          <div class="input-field col s12">
            <textarea id="welcomeMessage" name="welcomeMessage" class="materialize-textarea" value="{{proposal.welcomeMessage}}"></textarea>
            <label for="welcomeMessage">Welcome Message</label>
          </div>
          <p>Below you can give your customer any insights on how they will be reedeming this offer</p>
          <div class="input-field col s12">
            <textarea id="redemptionInstructions" name="redemptionInstructions" class="materialize-textarea" value="{{proposal.redemptionInstructions}}"></textarea>
            <label for="redemptionInstructions">Redemption Instructions</label>
          </div>
          <label>Tags</label>
          <div class="input-field">
            <input type="text" data-role="materialtags" name="tags" value="{{tag}}" id="tags">
            {{!-- <label for="tags">Tags</label> --}}
            <div id="suggesstion-box" style="border: 1px solid black;
                    padding: 9px 10px 4px;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                    display:none"><span id="suggesstion-inner"></span></div>
            {{#if tags}}
            Recent tags: <br />
            {{/if}}
            {{#each tags}}
            {{#if this}}
            <div class="chip recenttags" for="tags" style="cursor: pointer">
              {{this}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            {{/each}}
          </div>
          {{!-- text area input-field --}}
          {{!-- <div class="input-field col s12">
            <textarea id="textarea1" class="materialize-textarea"></textarea>
            <label for="offerMessage">Textarea</label>
          </div> --}}
          {{!-- text area end input field --}}
          <input type="button" value="Save" class="btn primary" onclick="$('#editproposal').submit()">
          <button data-target="deleteModal" class="btn red modal-trigger">Delete</button>
      </form>
      {{!-- delete button --}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="deleteModal" class="modal modal-fixed-footer">
    <div class="modal-content">
    <p>Are you sure you want to delete this proposal? The trash goblins will never give it back!</p>
    <div class="modal-footer">
      <form action="/proposals/{{proposal.id}}?_method=DELETE" method="post" id="delete-form">
        <input type="hidden" name="_method" value ="DELETE">
        <button type="submit" class="btn red"><i class="fa fa-remove"></i>Delete</button>
        <a href="#!" class="modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">Close</a>
      </form>
      {{!-- <form class="proposal_add-wrapper" method="post" action="/proposals/voteUser/{{proposal.id}}">
        <div>
          <input name="voteBody" type="submit" value="Accept" class="btn green lighten-1">
          <a href="#!" class="modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">Close</a>
        </div>
      </form> --}}
    </div>
  </div>

